content:
balance as at 30-Sep-2022 represented:

CNY30.5M of Others subtotal, including CNY25.5M of 暫估成本 (estimated costs), CNY4.8M of Company #2, and CNY2199K of Deposit subtotal
CNY85.2M of Related party payables Subtotal, primarily consisting of CNY83.0M from 股權投資基金合夥企業(有限合夥) (Equity Investment Fund Partnership) and CNY2.2M from 物流倉儲有限公司 (Logistics Warehouse Co., Ltd.)

SUMMARY: Used entities 'Others subtotal' (CNY30.5M) and 'Related party payables Subtotal' (CNY85.2M) with major components including 暫估成本, Company #2, Deposit subtotal, 股權投資基金合夥企業, and 物流倉儲有限公司. Total payables: CNY121.0M.
